To-day App Store description

- to-do list
- resets every morning at 5 AM
- focus on tasks that need to be done today
- tasks are done more easily if written down
- Clear view of what needs to be done today

To-day is a daily to-do list app. The list resets every morning at 5 AM to give
you a fresh start of the day. You only want to put tasks on the list that you
need or want to do today. 
